modName: Rogue Race based on Sasuke Sword Style
summary: Rogue Race based on Sasuke Sword Style, have a unique swords position.
descriptionHtml:
Rogue Race based on Sasuke Sword Style, have a unique swords position.
They come to Skyrim to seek power, to kill a certain man.
Specialist at one handed weapon and destruction magic.

New Version 1.1 Swords now more closer to the body, for light armor user.

If you want to know who the man that Rogue want to kill, download this [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28779] Itachi and Kisame from Akatsuki [/url] mod
